    "summary": "The user expresses profound guilt and suicidal ideation, framing their potential death as a \"kindness\" or \"favor\" to their family to alleviate their burden. The assistant consistently provides empathetic validation of the user's feelings while explicitly rejecting the idea that self-harm is a solution and directing the user toward professional help.",
